Create an Sql warehouse

Serverless SQL warehouses are faster, cost-effective, secure, and start instantly.
They are hosted and managed by Databricks and include all the features of Pro.


--- create a catalog --
catalog is the top level container -- mamnages schemas,tables view permissiions
Use GRANT to manage permission
Simplifies governance across multiple workspaces

Creata a Catalog
CREATE CATALOG sales_catalog
COMMENT "Catalog for managing sales data";

